talents.bio:
Experienced Senior Software Engineer with over 9 years in mobile development,
specializing in Android and Flutter. Skilled in using AI tools to boost coding efficiency and bring new ideas to app development. Passionate about leading
complex projects, contributing to open-source communities, and mentoring junior
engineers to foster team growth and deliver high-quality mobile apps. My expertise
includes hands-on development in Kotlin Multiplatform and Flutter and recent
exploration into AWS.
